{"tid":2390792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中不明　香港經濟體非常複雜　一日在中國下或一部份　經濟不會好","createTime":"2021-02-01T20:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T21:20:12.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4951e582aed49f4ae8e2090faec5d6ea353567e8","tid":2390792,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T20:57:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://disp.cc/b/163-89Rh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisp.cc%2Fb%2F163-89Rh&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=34ddfcc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://disp.cc/b/163-89Rh</a><br />\n<br />\n香港是個十分複雜纖細的經濟體系, 但意識到這點的人卻不多.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://b.bbi.com.tw/Gossiping/1K_doKHS.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fb.bbi.com.tw%2FGossiping%2F1K_doKHS.html&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=d7cac133\" target=\"_blank\">http://b.bbi.com.tw/Gossiping/1K_doKHS.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中華人民共和國希望像英國一樣, 以控制買辦階級, 去管治整個香港.<br />\n<br />\n大陸長期對香港的看法, 就是殖民地, 教育中多數有「殖民地就是侵略者控制<br />\n買辦走狗政治」這樣的印象, 當自己有一天能當統治者時, 便誤以為只要跟英<br />\n國一樣控制買辦走狗, 這裡就能如殖民時代一樣穩固."},{"pid":"4ff467be61f15d53d302f89027531374d32d9e7b","tid":2390792,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T21:20:12.000Z","msg":"共產黨樣樣急功近利，未學行先學走<br />\n真正接觸西方文化有幾耐？廿年都俾多佢<br />\n對金融科技醫藥...通通一知半解"}]}